Domain

public static final String Domain
Domain. Allowed characters are alpha numeric and dash. Domain can have between two and 127 levels. Each level can contain between one and 63 characters.

See Also:

URL

public static final String URL
URL. Allowed characters are alpha numeric and: .&+/=?#\. Percentage can only be used preceding two valid HEX characters.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

CreditCard

public static final String CreditCard
Credit card. Allowed characters are numeric spaces and dashes. The format must be four groups of four digits each. They may have space or dash between the groups.
